{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you-- we would sell a shirt or pants or something for-- for additional food-- for sugar, for-- which, naturally, was one of the things if you were caught, you would be hanged.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- Did you change-- exchange clothing for food?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was the only way you could survive there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, you would die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- you-- you were full of lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were full of bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- them bunks-- there was straw laying on, about half a foot thick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was just crawling with-- with-- with-- with insects.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Your entertainment at night would be sitting there to crack the lice in your undershirt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then I mentioned before that potbelly stove there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would use that to cook extra food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somebody would watch on the door, whether some of the guards would come into the camp at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we would-- there, we would cook potatoes or whatever we had.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was the additional food we would get.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one thing was in this-- all the camps, there was hardly anybody would steal anything, even when you were hungry because everybody was in the same situation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What was bad in the camp is some people, especially [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] high-- educated intellectual, they would kill themselves right away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They would hang themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a lot of them would get sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when you'd get sick there-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I would say over 90% you wouldn't see anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They would be brought into a so-called hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that hospital was just people to die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The ones what could not walk would be loaded into so-called ambulances.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "God darn-it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm talking too much.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
